A preferred embodiment of the present invention will now be described by way of example only with reference to the accompanying drawings, in which:


FIG. 1 illustrates a cross-sectional view along the longitudinal axis of a fluid control valve in accordance with an embodiment of the present invention, shown coupled to a control motor and a ventilator enclosure;


FIG. 2 illustrates a side view of the valve and control motor as shown in FIG. 1 (the view from the other side being a mirror image);


FIG. 3 illustrates a view along direction X of one end of the valve and control motor illustrated in FIG. 1, shown coupled to a blower;


FIG. 4 illustrates a view along direction Y of the other end of the valve and control motor illustrated in FIG. 1;


FIG. 5 illustrates a view along direction X of one end of the rotary valve member of the valve illustrated in FIG. 1;


FIG. 6 illustrates a view along direction Y of the other end of the rotary valve member of the valve illustrated in FIG. 1; and


FIGS. 7(a-d) illustrate examples of the pressure pulse waveforms which can be achieved by the fluid valve of the present invention.
